  <title>
    Introductory Set Theory
  </title>

  <introduction>
    <p>
      In this chapter, we lay the groundwork for our exposition of real analysis. We will introduce the fundamental notions of sets, relations, and functions, which underlie not only all of analysis but also all of modern mathematics as well.
    </p>
  </introduction>

